      "fontSize": 17.387755102040817,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "• Explicit emergency language: \"chest pain\", \"fallen\", \"can't breathe\", \"help me\"\n• Triggers Emergency Lobster Workflow:\n  (a) Notify all caregivers (b) Send address (c) Display emergency number\n❌ Does NOT call emergency services autonomously (requires human confirmation)",
