      "originalText": "✅ Consent Layer: Explicit recorded consent (voice/tap) for each data processing category\n✅ Data Minimisation: LLM receives only context required for immediate task\n✅ Right to Erasure: \"Forget Everything\" command → Full deletion across all layers + signed certificate\n✅ Data Residency: Indian data centres (Mumbai/Hyderabad AWS) for enterprise/healthcare tiers",
